[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:03.381 --> 00:00:11.130 align:middle line:90%


00:00:11.130 --> 00:00:15.020 align:middle line:10%
>>If you want to discover
bizarre, alien forms,

00:00:15.020 --> 00:00:17.930 align:middle line:10%
strange creatures
from far, far away,

