from a bottle to catch a crab

00:04:11.450 --> 00:04:12.690 align:middle line:90%
is child's play.

00:04:12.690 --> 00:04:16.010 align:middle line:84%
It's almost exactly like lifting
a rock to find a delicious

00:04:16.010 --> 00:04:17.390 align:middle line:90%
morsel underneath.

00:04:17.390 --> 00:04:20.930 align:middle line:90%
It does it by instinct.

00:04:20.930 --> 00:04:23.500 align:middle line:84%
