how the octopus will

00:08:08.210 --> 00:08:11.326 align:middle line:90%
deal with the problem.

00:08:11.326 --> 00:08:14.679 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:08:14.679 --> 00:08:18.040 align:middle line:90%


